"><h1 id=3D"analyze-images">Analyze images</h1>
<p>Azure AI Vision is an artificial intelligence capability that enables so=
ftware systems to interpret visual input by analyzing images. In Microsoft =
Azure, the <strong>Vision</strong> Azure AI service provides pre-built mode=
ls for common computer vision tasks, including analysis of images to sugges=
t captions and tags, detection of common objects and people. You can also u=
se the Azure AI Vision service to remove the background or create a foregro=
und matting of images.</p>
<blockquote>
  <p><strong>Note</strong>: This exercise is based on pre-release SDK softw=
are, which may be subject to change. Where necessary, we've used specific v=
ersions of packages; which may not reflect the latest available versions. Y=
